data.text:
Jasdan, Gujarat, India

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 22.035608, 71.201775.

Jasdan is a large municipality in the very central part of Gujarat, located about 37 miles southeast from the city of Rajkot. There are about 40,000 people living now in Jasdan, and it is a center of Saurashtra culture. There are a few colleges and a new modern hospital in the town. Tourists come to visit the town in order to enjoy some beautiful views to the neighboring small rivers and hills.
